Anda bisa membawanya pulang.

00:12:42.600 --> 00:12:44.640
Tuhan Krishna, terima kasih.

00:12:45.040 --> 00:12:45.920
Terima kasih.

00:13:05.720 --> 00:13:06.800
Mohan.

00:13:08.000 --> 00:13:10.880
Hari yang sangat
kami tunggu-tunggu

00:13:12.160 --> 00:13:13.640
akhirnya tiba di sini!

00:13:20.200 --> 00:13:23.920
Hari ini, kami akan menghukum
pelaku kesalahan Gungun.

00:13:25.480 --> 00:13:26.640
Ya, Radha.

00:13:34.040 --> 00:13:34.920
Ayo, ayo pergi.

